{"type": "article", "id": 30700, "title": "智能保温杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-07T22:52:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/201608072133547dh8pa3P54oiAbEw.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>在饮料的世界里，再细小的温度差都会带来口感上的变化。为了让人喝到温度刚刚好的饮料，Eric Fields 和 Martin Gschwandtl 共同研发了一款名为 <a href=\"https://embertech.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ember Mug</a> 的智能保温杯，可以让饮料长时间保持在用户设定的温度下。调整温度时只需要旋转保温杯底部即可，除此之外也可以通过配套的应用进行预设，还能在华氏/摄氏两种温标间进行切换。这是它的<a href=\"https://store.embertech.com/cart/11856634307:1\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 149 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807213409z4wNgdpIajZvirkG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807213409ozLvwWjnCbNy5YpP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807213410SeNxGgDWpP1t3wJf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.810476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807213409n0XWi5DGrjRZg83L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}